    {
      "name": "API Mobile",
      "description": "Endpoints consommés par l'app Flutter. Auth Sanctum guard `mobile` + OTP statique 123456 en dev. À swapper contre un middleware Supabase JWT en prod.\n\n## Flow\n\n1. POST /auth/request-otp { indicatif, numero } → log OTP (dev_hint=123456).\n2. POST /auth/verify-otp { indicatif, numero, otp, nom?, prenom?, date_naissance? } → token + user. Si l'user n'existe pas, nom+prenom+date_naissance sont requis (sign-up).\n3. Tous les endpoints suivants : header `Authorization: Bearer {{mobile_token}}` (variable Postman, à set manuellement après step 2).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Auth",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "POST /api/mobile/auth/request-otp",
              "description": "Déclenche l'envoi OTP. En dev, retourne `dev_hint: \"123456\"` dans le body.",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"indicatif\": \"+241\",\n  \"numero\": \"077123456\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/mobile/auth/request-otp", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "mobile", "auth", "request-otp"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "POST /api/mobile/auth/verify-otp",
              "description": "Vérifie l'OTP (123456 en dev). Si l'user existe pour ce numéro → login. Sinon sign-up : nom + prenom + date_naissance requis.\n\nLa réponse contient `token` à coller dans la variable Postman `mobile_token`.",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "type": "text/javascript",
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                      "  const j = pm.response.json();",
                      "  if (j.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('mobile_token', j.token);",
                      "}"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"indicatif\": \"+241\",\n  \"numero\": \"077123456\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\",\n  \"nom\": \"Test\",\n  \"prenom\": \"Mobile\",\n  \"date_naissance\": \"1990-01-15\"\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/mobile/auth/verify-otp", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "mobile", "auth", "verify-otp"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "GET /api/mobile/auth/me",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{mobile_token}}" }
                ],
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/mobile/auth/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "mobile", "auth", "me"] }
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "POST /api/mobile/auth/logout",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{mobile_token}}" }
                ],
                "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/mobile/auth/logout", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "mobile", "auth", "logout"] }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Profil",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "GET /api/mobile/profil",
